data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and space in this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the heart of Dandridge, TN! Situated on a generous 0.76-acre lot. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and spacious living area, perfect for both relaxation and entertaining. The great room offers gorgeous cathedral ceiling and wood beams. The well-appointed kitchen boasts stainless appliances and solid surface countertops, making it a hub for culinary creativity. The double door pantry is quite unique. The primary suite offers Tile Shower, double vanity and soaking tub. What sets this property apart is its expansive deck, an entertainer's dream that extends the living space outdoors. Picture hosting memorable gatherings, enjoying summer barbecues, or simply unwinding in the fresh air, or take a dip on a hot summer's day in the above ground pool. Beyond the comforts of the home, discover an added perk for electric vehicle enthusiasts - a dedicated Tesla charging station in the main level garage. 1196 sq ft of Unfinished Basement is awaiting your creative touch, imagine the possibilities:  gameroom area, home gym or additional living space.  This beauty is one mile from beautiful Douglas Lake and the public boat launch and just minutes to Pigeon Forge, Gatlinburg, the Great Smoky Mountains, as well as Knoxville.
